Description:

Cross Before the Crown by Paul Godfrey, 2012-10-06:
No reward comes without sacrifice. What will you need to sacrifice to be saved? In a word: everything. Count the cost.
-----------------------------------------------------------

It's Not A Social Club by Paul Godfrey:
Why do you go to church? Is it to chat about the week with people? What is Church for? This sermonette answers what Church should be for a Christian.
------------------------------------------------------------

It is a Social Club? by Ben Jones, 2012-09-26:
Often there are seeming contradictions in the bible. This is one of those times. We are not to have &quot;undue familiarity&quot; but we are to be &quot;highly social&quot;. This sermon is one side of the coin and ties everything together well at the end. If you wish to understand the full balance, watch this in conjunction with It's not a social club. &lt;a href=&quot;
